---
// Two-regime mempool: VDF (N<15) → Threshold (N≥15) with hysteresis at N=10
---
<figure class="adm-diagram" aria-label="Two-regime encrypted mempool">
  <svg viewBox="0 0 860 280" preserveAspectRatio="xMidYMid meet" role="img" aria-labelledby="mp-title mp-desc">
    <title id="mp-title">Two-regime encrypted mempool</title>
    <desc id="mp-desc">Time-lock VDF below N=15 validators, threshold encryption at and above; hysteresis switches back to VDF below N=10.</desc>
    <style>
      .d-text { font-family: "Instrument Serif", Georgia, serif; }
      .d-mono { font-family: "Geist Mono", "SF Mono", Menlo, monospace; }
      .d-eyebrow { font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.14em; opacity: 0.6; }
      .d-small   { font-size: 10.5px; opacity: 0.55; letter-spacing: 0.06em; }
    </style>

    <!-- VDF region -->
    <rect x="60" y="80" width="380" height="100" fill="var(--paper-3)" stroke="currentColor"/>
    <text x="250" y="118" text-anchor="middle" class="d-mono d-eyebrow" fill="currentColor">REGIME A</text>
    <text x="250" y="148" text-anchor="middle" class="d-text" font-size="24" fill="currentColor">Time-lock VDF</text>

    <!-- Threshold region -->
    <rect x="440" y="80" width="380" height="100" fill="var(--ink)"/>
    <text x="630" y="118" text-anchor="middle" class="d-mono d-eyebrow" fill="var(--paper)" opacity="0.7">REGIME B</text>
    <text x="630" y="148" text-anchor="middle" class="d-text" font-size="24" fill="var(--paper)">Threshold encryption</text>

    <!-- axis -->
    <line x1="60" y1="200" x2="820" y2="200" stroke="currentColor"/>
    <g class="d-mono" fill="currentColor" font-size="11" letter-spacing="0.08em">
      <text x="60"  y="225" text-anchor="middle">N=7</text>
      <text x="290" y="225" text-anchor="middle">N=10</text>
      <text x="440" y="225" text-anchor="middle">N=15</text>
      <text x="640" y="225" text-anchor="middle">N=30</text>
      <text x="820" y="225" text-anchor="middle">N=75</text>
    </g>
    <g stroke="currentColor">
      <line x1="60"  y1="195" x2="60"  y2="205"/>
      <line x1="290" y1="195" x2="290" y2="205"/>
      <line x1="440" y1="195" x2="440" y2="205"/>
      <line x1="640" y1="195" x2="640" y2="205"/>
      <line x1="820" y1="195" x2="820" y2="205"/>
    </g>

    <!-- boundary lines -->
    <line x1="440" y1="60" x2="440" y2="200" stroke="currentColor" stroke-dasharray="4 4"/>
    <text x="440" y="50" text-anchor="middle" class="d-mono" font-size="10" letter-spacing="0.10em" fill="currentColor">switch up at N=15</text>

    <line x1="290" y1="60" x2="290" y2="200" stroke="currentColor" stroke-dasharray="4 4" opacity="0.5"/>
    <text x="290" y="50" text-anchor="middle" class="d-mono" font-size="10" letter-spacing="0.10em" fill="currentColor" opacity="0.7">switch back at N&lt;10</text>

    <!-- captions -->
    <g fill="currentColor" class="d-mono d-small">
      <text x="250" y="258" text-anchor="middle">Wesolowski VDF · no DKG needed</text>
      <text x="630" y="258" text-anchor="middle">BLS threshold · DKG-coordinated</text>
    </g>
  </svg>
  <figcaption class="adm-diagram-caption">Encrypted mempool · WP §8.4</figcaption>
</figure>

<style>
  .adm-diagram { margin: 24px 0; border: 1px solid var(--rule); background: var(--paper); color: var(--ink); }
  .adm-diagram svg { display: block; width: 100%; height: auto; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }
  .adm-diagram > svg { padding: 24px; }
  .adm-diagram-caption { border-top: 1px solid var(--rule); padding: 10px 18px; font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 10.5px; letter-spacing: 0.10em; text-transform: uppercase; color: var(--ink-3); background: var(--paper-2); }
</style>
